Package: AACloudTools
Type: Package
Title: Simplify the use of various cloud resources (S3 storage, Redshift, on-
    demand clusters...)
Version: 0.7.6
Author: Christopher Lewis
Maintainer: Marc Veillet <marc.veillet@ihsmarkit.com>
Description: Collection of functions to use of various cloud resources. For
    example... ... to store or retrieve files in S3 storage ... to query data
    on Redshift, to download tables in Redshift etc. ... to launch on-demand AWS
    instances and clusters ... etc.
